name: 2022 The 3rd International Conference on Robotics Systems and Vehicle Technology
content: Publication: Accepted papers with registration and presentation will be published in the International Conference Proceedings Series by ACM with ISBN: 978-1-4503-9678-3, which will be archived in the ACM Digital Library, and indexed by Ei Compendex, Scopus and submitted to be reviewed by Thomson Reuters Conference Proceedings Citation Index (ISI Web of Science).
